title: Jinx free week?
body: Uh so apparently {{champion:222}} is in free week? It doesn't officially say she is in free week on the site and i can't access her while playing so a bug? The photo is not uploading but does anyone else have the same issue?

replies.body: Free week champ bugs are weird. Best of just submitting a [support ticket](https://support.leagueoflegends.com/anonymous_requests/new) to get it fixed ASAP.
